268
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:46,290
Stop wasting your effort.

269
00:18:02,290 --> 00:18:06,100
- Little Fairy!
- My baby is the best!

270
00:18:06,100 --> 00:18:08,260
Let's draw an even better one next time

271
00:18:08,260 --> 00:18:11,320
