387
00:24:54,090 --> 00:24:55,540
Xiao Qi.

388
00:24:55,540 --> 00:24:59,740
When you show so little sincerity, what can I do for you?

389
00:25:01,030 --> 00:25:03,610
I'm really sorry, President Xu. I-I...

390
00:25:03,610 --> 00:25:05,500
I have a low tolerance for alcohol.

391
00:25:05,500 --> 00:25:09,580
That's for later. You show your sincerity first.

392
00:25:10,420 --> 00:25:12,830
Xiao Qi, you're not a rookie

393
00:25:12,830 --> 00:25:14,670
